  "title": "Business Development Executive (Automotive Products/ Export Sales)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Drive sales growth for automotive products such as tyres, rims, and batteries across assigned international markets.</li><li>Identify and develop new business opportunities with overseas distributors and customers to expand market presence.</li><li>Manage and support existing international accounts to achieve individual and team sales targets.</li><li>Coordinate and follow through on sales orders, ensuring smooth order processing, delivery timelines, and customer satisfaction.</li><li>Monitor sales activities, track order status, and resolve issues related to fulfilment or documentation.</li><li>Work closely with internal teams to support pricing, quotations, and sales-related documentation.</li><li>Analyse market trends, customer needs, and competitor activity to support sales and market strategies.</li><li>Participate in overseas business trips when required to strengthen client relationships and\nexplore new markets.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Business, Administration, or a related discipline.</li><li>At least <strong>1 year of experience</strong> in international sales, export sales, or business development.</li><li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office (especially Excel and PowerPoint), with good commercial awareness and analytical ability; comfortable in a desk-based role with occasional overseas travel.</li></ul><p>Please submit your updated resume in Word format by using the <strong>Apply Now Button.</strong><br />We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<br />Email resume to <strong>ken.ng@peopleprofilers.com</strong><br />People Profilers Pte Ltd, 20 Cecil Street, #08-09, PLUS Building, Singapore 049705.<br />Tel: 6950 9724<br /><a href=\"http://www.peopleprofilers.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http://www.peopleprofilers.com</a>\nEA License Number: 02C4944\nRegistration Number: R1872398<br />Posting Personnel: Ng Jwee Ken<br />Ref: 5WYVY5VR</p>",
